\f1\b\fs32 \cf0 INTRO\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs21 \cf0 What if God isn\'92t interested in your perfection as much as you pursuing Him?\
What if salvation is something more than fire insurance?\
What if this collection of books is more than just a collection of stories we should read and apply simple moralistic ideals to our lives in the hopes that we will achieve what we want in life?\
What if being saved isn\'92t\'92 just an event that happens to us?\
What if you get saved and you remain the same?\
What if you come forward and it doesn\'92t take? Or you don\'92t feel any different? Or even worse what if you did it wrong?\
What if give your life to Christ and nothing changes?  You\'92re still addicted, you\'92re struggling\'85He didn\'92t fix it like you were told.\
What if you\'92re struggling in your faith with the wrong things?\
What if doubt is the very thing needed to have faith and what if faith and doubt go together?\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf2 Transition: \'a0Today we\'92re wrapping up our series Unqualified and so far we\'92ve said this\'85\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs21 \cf0 Recap series up to this point\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God has taken a broken man who pretended to be someone else to get what he wanted and what we\'92ve said so far is this:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God can\'92t bless who you pretend to be.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is in love with who I am this day, not who I\'92ll be some day\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Many times in life we miss what is possible because we only see what is mis_ing.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We need to have the right conversation\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

