\f3\b\fs18 \super 28\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Then the man said, \'93Your name\'a0will no longer be Jacob, but Israel,
\fs15 \super [f]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0because you have struggled with God and with humans and have overcome.\'94\
\

\f3\b\fs18 \super 29\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jacob said, \'93Please tell me your name.\'94  Gen 32\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f4 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Wait\'85Jacob\'85No God just changed his name\'85He\'92s someone different\'85he\'92s a new person\'85he\'92s not Jacob anymore\'85he\'92s Israel.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But as you read it rarely if ever refers to him as Israel\'85until 3 chapters later it says this\'85\
