\f3\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 14\'a0
\f5\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jacob set up a stone pillar\'a0at the place where God had talked with him, and he poured out a drink offering\'a0on it; he also poured oil on it.\'a0  Gen 35\
