\f3\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 33\'a0
\f5\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When Jacob had finished giving instructions to his sons, he drew his feet up into the bed, breathed his last and was gathered to his people.  Gen 49\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f2\fs21 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This drove me crazy forever\'85what is the author trying to do here.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What is happening.  One moment he is Jacob and the next he is Israel. \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}One moment he is the man who wrestled with God and won\'85and the next he is deceiver.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I spent literally months thinking about this processing this bugged over and over about why it was written this way until it hit me\'85it\'92s a process!  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What is being communicated is we think salvation is a moment\'85but it isn\'92t\'85it\'92s a process.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That one day he was Jacob and then the next he was Israel\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He has seasons where he was wrestling with God and growing in his faith and he had seasons where he wasn\'92t.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It wasn\'92t a quick fix but it was the start of something unique in his life where God was redefining who he was and how others saw him.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
